# Smart Resume Analyzer

A Flask-based Smart Resume Analyzer that analyzes resumes by matching resume keywords with job descriptions and calculates a match score percentage.

## Features

- Upload Resume (PDF)
- Enter Job Description
- Keyword Matching
- Match Score Percentage
- Simple UI

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Flask
- HTML
- CSS
- PyPDF2

## Installation

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/smart-resume-analyzer.git

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run application:

python app.py

Open browser:

http://127.0.0.1:5000
